ing: salt and freshly ground pepper to taste
n: Raw Zucchini Salad with Tomato and Basil
des: "A light summer salad with raw zucchini, tomatoes, and basil with a simple olive oil and vinegar dressing to bring out the flavor of the vegetables. It tastes best with farm fresh vegetables from your local market or your yard."
ins: Combine zucchini and tomatoes in a salad bowl. Whisk oil, vinegar, salt, and pepper together until well combined. Pour over vegetables and toss. Let sit for 15 minutes. Sprinkle with basil right before serving.
